OL,3,CScientific breakthrough in dementia
OL,4,Cdiagnosis after 10 years research
OL,6,FScientists in Southampton have
OL,7,Fdeveloped a new test which can reduce
OL,8,Fthe time of getting a dementia
OL,9,Fdiagnosis from years to a matter of
OL,10,Fminutes.
OL,12,FThe new test, using lasers, is being
OL,13,Fhailed as a significant breakthrough
OL,14,Fin medical technology that will
OL,15,Fbenefit thousands of patients.
OL,17,FResearchers at the University of
OL,18,FSouthampton have taken ten years to
OL,19,Fdevelop a system where they shine
OL,20,Fmultiple lasers on a drop of blood.
