OL,3,CScientific breakthrough in dementia
OL,4,Cdiagnosis after 10 years research
OL,6,FThe blood is then analysed by a
OL,7,Fcomputer programme, which not only
OL,8,Fdetects whether the patient has
OL,9,Fdementia, but also if someone might
OL,10,Fdevelop the disease in the future -
OL,11,Fand what type of dementia it would be.
OL,13,FProf Sumeet Mahajan from the
OL,14,FUniversity of Southampton said: "No
OL,15,Fone has ever approached it in this
OL,16,Fmanner.
OL,18,FWhat is different is that we are not
OL,19,Flooking at one single component, not
OL,20,Fone protein or one marker, we look at
OL,21,Feverything.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/6
