OL,3,CScientific breakthrough in dementia
OL,4,Cdiagnosis after 10 years research
OL,6,F"We look at whatever is contained in
OL,7,Fthat drop of blood, protein, sugar,
OL,8,Ffat or lipids or metabolites and the
OL,9,Fvarying concentration of that
OL,10,Fcomposition tells us what might be
OL,11,Fhappening."
OL,13,FThe research is called the Hope
OL,14,Fproject because an early test to
OL,15,Fidentify whether someone has, or will
OL,16,Fget dementia many years before
OL,17,Fsymptoms start to develop, will have
OL,18,Fhuge benefits for treatment.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/6
