OL,4,Cdiagnosis after 10 years research
OL,6,FThe new test is also cheaper than any
OL,7,Fother diagnostic test for dementia
OL,8,Fcurrently available. Also, just in the
OL,9,Fsmall test samples so far, the success
OL,10,Frate is 97%.
OL,12,FMore clinical trials will take place,
OL,13,Fand then investment is needed to raise
OL,14,Fawareness and produce the portable
OL,15,Ftest kits, which is hoped to take
OL,16,Fplace within the next five years.
